{
    "invoice": {
        "headline": "Invoice Transmission",
        "desc": "",
        "fields": {
            "invoice.option": {
                "label": "Invoice Transmission Options",
                "desc": "<p>Here you can choose whether and how you want to transmit your invoices to _#_platformName_#_.\n    The following options are available:<\/p>\n\n<ul>\n    <li><p>Do not transmit invoices to _#_platformName_#_<\/p>\n        <p>If you select this option, your invoices will not be transmitted to _#_platformName_#_. This means:\n            You organize the provision of invoices yourself.<\/p>\n    <\/li>\n    <li>\n        <p> Invoices created in the webshop will be transmitted to _#_platformName_#_ <\/p>\n        <p> If your shop system has the ability to create invoices, these will be\n            automatically uploaded to _#_platformName_#_ every 60 minutes. <\/p>\n    <\/li>\n    <li><p>Invoices created by third-party systems (e.g. ERP system) will be transmitted to _#_platformName_#_<\/p>\n        <p>Invoices that you create with your third-party system (e.g. ERP) can be uploaded to your\n            webshop server, retrieved by magnalister and uploaded to _#_platformName_#_. More\n            information appears after selecting this option in the info icon under &ldquo;Settings for the transmission\n            of invoices created from a third-party system [...]&rdquo;.<\/p>\n    <\/li>\n    <li>\n        <p>magnalister should take over invoice creation and transmit to _#_platformName_#_<\/p>\n        <p>Select this option if magnalister should take over the creation and transmission of invoices for you.\n            To do this, fill in the fields under &ldquo;Data for invoice generation\n            by\n            magnalister&rdquo;. The transfer takes place every #xx# minutes.<\/p>\n    <\/li>\n<\/ul>",
                "key": "_#_platform_#_.invoice.option",
                "type": "selection",
                "values": {
                    "off": "Do not transmit invoices to _#_platformName_#_",
                    "webshop": "Invoices created in the webshop will be transmitted to _#_platformName_#_",
                    "erp": "Invoices created by ERP will be transmitted to _#_platformName_#_",
                    "magna": "Invoice creation and transmission is done by magnalister"
                },
                "cssClasses": [
                    "ml-uploadInvoiceOption"
                ],
                "submit": "Invoice.Option"
            }
        }
    },
    "magnalisterinvoice": {
        "headline": "Data for invoice generation by magnalister",
        "desc": "",
        "cssClasses": [
            "ml-magnalisterInvoiceGenerator"
        ],
        "fields": {
            "invoice.invoicedir": {
                "label": "Transmitted invoices",
                "buttontext": "Display",
                "key": "_#_platform_#_.invoice.invoicedir",
                "rowCssClasses": [
                    "ml-magnalisterInvoiceGenerator"
                ],
                "type": "html",
                "settings": {
                    "save": false
                }
            },
            "invoice.mailcopy": {
                "label": "Invoice copy to",
                "hint": "Enter your email address here to receive a copy of the uploaded invoice by email.",
                "key": "_#_platform_#_.invoice.mailcopy",
                "rowCssClasses": [
                    "ml-magnalisterInvoiceGenerator"
                ],
                "type": "text",
                "submit": "Invoice.MailCopy"
            },
            "invoice.invoiceprefix": {
                "label": "Invoice number prefix",
                "hint": "If you enter a prefix here, it will be placed before the invoice number. Example: R10000. Invoices generated by magnalister start with the number 10000.",
                "key": "_#_platform_#_.invoice.invoiceprefix",
                "rowCssClasses": [
                    "ml-magnalisterInvoiceGenerator"
                ],
                "type": "text",
                "default": "R",
                "submit": "Invoice.InvoicePrefix"
            },
            "invoice.reversalinvoiceprefix": {
                "label": "Credit note prefix",
                "hint": "If you enter a prefix here, it will be placed before the credit note number. Example: S20000. Credit notes generated by magnalister start with the number 20000.",
                "key": "_#_platform_#_.invoice.reversalinvoiceprefix",
                "rowCssClasses": [
                    "ml-magnalisterInvoiceGenerator"
                ],
                "type": "text",
                "default": "S",
                "submit": "Invoice.ReversalInvoicePrefix"
            },
            "invoice.companyadressleft": {
                "label": "Company address field (left)",
                "key": "_#_platform_#_.invoice.companyadressleft",
                "rowCssClasses": [
                    "ml-magnalisterInvoiceGenerator"
                ],
                "type": "text",
                "submit": "Invoice.CompanyAddressLeft"
            },
            "invoice.companyadressright": {
                "label": "Address information block (right)",
                "key": "_#_platform_#_.invoice.companyadressright",
                "rowCssClasses": [
                    "ml-magnalisterInvoiceGenerator"
                ],
                "type": "textarea",
                "submit": "Invoice.CompanyAddressRight"
            },
            "invoice.headline": {
                "label": "Invoice heading",
                "key": "_#_platform_#_.invoice.headline",
                "rowCssClasses": [
                    "ml-magnalisterInvoiceGenerator"
                ],
                "type": "text",
                "submit": "Invoice.Headline"
            },
            "invoice.invoicehintheadline": {
                "label": "Invoice notes heading",
                "key": "_#_platform_#_.invoice.invoicehintheadline",
                "rowCssClasses": [
                    "ml-magnalisterInvoiceGenerator"
                ],
                "type": "text",
                "submit": "Invoice.InvoiceHintHeadline"
            },
            "invoice.invoicehinttext": {
                "label": "Note text",
                "key": "_#_platform_#_.invoice.invoicehinttext",
                "rowCssClasses": [
                    "ml-magnalisterInvoiceGenerator"
                ],
                "type": "textarea",
                "submit": "Invoice.InvoiceHintText"
            },
            "invoice.footercell1": {
                "label": "Footer column 1",
                "key": "_#_platform_#_.invoice.footercell1",
                "rowCssClasses": [
                    "ml-magnalisterInvoiceGenerator"
                ],
                "type": "textarea",
                "submit": "Invoice.FooterCell1"
            },
            "invoice.footercell2": {
                "label": "Footer column 2",
                "key": "_#_platform_#_.invoice.footercell2",
                "rowCssClasses": [
                    "ml-magnalisterInvoiceGenerator"
                ],
                "type": "textarea",
                "submit": "Invoice.FooterCell2"
            },
            "invoice.footercell3": {
                "label": "Footer column 3",
                "key": "_#_platform_#_.invoice.footercell3",
                "rowCssClasses": [
                    "ml-magnalisterInvoiceGenerator"
                ],
                "type": "textarea",
                "submit": "Invoice.FooterCell3"
            },
            "invoice.footercell4": {
                "label": "Footer column 4",
                "key": "_#_platform_#_.invoice.footercell4",
                "rowCssClasses": [
                    "ml-magnalisterInvoiceGenerator"
                ],
                "type": "textarea",
                "submit": "Invoice.FooterCell4"
            },
            "invoice.preview": {
                "label": "Invoice preview",
                "key": "_#_platform_#_.invoice.preview",
                "rowCssClasses": [
                    "ml-magnalisterInvoiceGenerator"
                ],
                "hint": "Here you can view a preview of your invoice with the data you have stored.",
                "type": "extern",
                "params": [],
                "procFunc": "MagnaCompatibleConfigure::invoicePreview"
            }
        }
    },
    "erpinvoice": {
        "headline": "Invoice transmission from ERP",
        "desc": "",
        "cssClasses": [
            "ml-erpInvoice"
        ],
        "fields": {
            "invoice.erpInvoiceSource": {
                "label": "Source folder for invoices (server path)",
                "desc": "<p>Select the server path to the folder where you upload the invoices from your third-party system (e.g. ERP) as PDF.  <\/p><p> <b>Important note<\/b>: In order for magnalister to assign a PDF invoice to a shop order, the PDF files must be named according to one of the following two patterns:<\/p><ol><li>Naming according to the shop order<\/p><p>Pattern: #shop-order-number#.pdf<\/p><p>Example:<br\/>Shop order number: 12345678<br\/>Invoice PDF should be: 12345678.pdf<\/p><\/li><li>Naming according to the shop order + invoice number from ERP system<\/p><p>Pattern:  #shop-order-number#_#invoice-number#.pdf<\/p><p>Example:<br>Shop order number: 12345678<br>Invoice number from ERP: 9876543<br>Invoice PDF should be: 12345678_9876543.pdf <\/p> <\/li> <\/ol>",
                "hint": "",
                "key": "_#_platform_#_.invoice.erpinvoicesource",
                "rowCssClasses": [
                    "ml-erpInvoice"
                ],
                "default": "Receipts/_#_platformName_#_/ToBeProcessed/Invoices",
                "type": "fileBrowser"
            },
            "invoice.erpInvoiceDestination": {
                "label": "Destination folder for invoices transmitted to _#_platformName_#_ (server path)",
                "desc": "<p>After magnalister has uploaded an invoice from the source folder to _#_platformName_#_, it is moved to the destination folder. This way you can track which invoices have already been transmitted to _#_platformName_#_.<\/p><p>Select the server path to the destination folder where the invoices uploaded to _#_platformName_#_ should be moved.<\/p><p><b>Important note:<\/b> If you do not select a different destination folder for invoices uploaded to _#_platformName_#_, you cannot see which invoices have already been uploaded to _#_platformName_#_<\/p>",
                "hint": "",
                "key": "_#_platform_#_.invoice.erpinvoicedestination",
                "rowCssClasses": [
                    "ml-erpInvoice"
                ],
                "default": "Receipts/_#_platformName_#_/Processed/Invoices",
                "type": "fileBrowser"
            },
            "invoice.erpReversalInvoiceSource": {
                "label": "Source folder for credit notes (server path)",
                "desc": "<p>Select the server path to the folder where you upload the credit notes from your third-party system (e.g. ERP) as PDF.  <\/p><p> <b>Important note<\/b>: In order for magnalister to assign a PDF credit note to a shop order, the PDF files must be named according to one of the following two patterns:<\/p><ol><li>Naming according to the shop order<\/p><p>Pattern: #shop-order-number#.pdf<\/p><p>Example:<br\/>Shop order number: 12345678<br\/>Credit note PDF should be: 12345678.pdf<\/p><\/li><li>Naming according to the shop order + credit note number from ERP system<\/p><p>Pattern:  #shop-order-number#_#credit-note-number#.pdf<\/p><p>Example:<br>Shop order number: 12345678<br>Credit note number from ERP: 9876543<br>Credit note PDF should be: 12345678_9876543.pdf  <\/li> <\/ol>",
                "hint": "",
                "key": "_#_platform_#_.invoice.erpreversalinvoicesource",
                "rowCssClasses": [
                    "ml-erpInvoice"
                ],
                "default": "Receipts/_#_platformName_#_/ToBeProcessed/CreditNote",
                "type": "fileBrowser"
            },
            "invoice.erpReversalInvoiceDestination": {
                "label": "Destination folder for credit notes transmitted to _#_platformName_#_ (server path)",
                "desc": "<p>After magnalister has uploaded a credit note from the source folder to _#_platformName_#_, it is moved to the destination folder. This way you can track which credit notes have already been transmitted to _#_platformName_#_.<\/p><p>Select the server path to the destination folder where the credit notes uploaded to _#_platformName_#_ should be moved.<\/p><p><b>Important note:<\/b> If you do not select a different destination folder for credit notes uploaded to _#_platformName_#_, you cannot see which credit notes have already been uploaded to _#_platformName_#_<\/p>",
                "hint": "",
                "key": "_#_platform_#_.invoice.erpreversalinvoicedestination",
                "rowCssClasses": [
                    "ml-erpInvoice"
                ],
                "default": "Receipts/_#_platformName_#_/Processed/CreditNote",
                "type": "fileBrowser"
            }
        }
    }
}